div.span: Value Living Welcome to eaves San Marcos – where sensible apartment living meets a sensible cost of living. We offer quality apartments in San Marcos that feature a few little extras, like well-equipped kitchens with brand name appliances and in-unit washers and dryers. Simply put, our San Marcos apartments offer more of what you hope for. Better than you bargained for. So, what are you waiting for? San Marcos Apartments by eaves While you choose to settle down in San Marcos, you deserve to come home to a place that feels comfortable and welcoming. At eaves San Marcos, that's exactly what you'll get. Located on Nordahl Road, our North County, our San Diego apartment community is conveniently located near Interstates 15 and 78, as well as the San Marcos Historical Society and Boehm Gallery of Palomar College. Residents can also sample mouth-watering cuisines from restaurants like Old California Restaurant Row, Fish House Vera Cruz and India Princess. San Marcos Apartment Community The best part of living in eaves San Marcos is access to a plethora of perks designed to complement your lifestyle and make your life more comfortable and convenient. Our technology package, eavesConnect, offers high-speed area WiFi, digital resident services including the ability to submit service requests and pay your rent online, Amazon package lockers, electronic locks and more. The moment you become a part of our San Diego community, you can instantly access perks that include free access to a fitness center and swimming pool and spa. You can even play a game tennis and basketball on our courts. Our professional staff will take care of any maintenance requests promptly and efficiently. Contact us to schedule an appointment and learn more about your new apartment in San Marcos today.

div.h2: this is the real deal. this is eaves.

a.div: Understanding what you value goes beyond offering you a quality apartment. It means having a respectful, friendly staff that you know you can depend on when you need them. Giving you one less thing to worry about and one more way to feel at home in your new community. That’s eaves.
We know you value convenience. That’s why all of our locations are also carefully selected to put you within reach of local shopping, restaurants and public transportation.

You made a promise to yourself to live within your means. That doesn't mean living without. Take advantage of our special resident discounts, early deposit refund program, and longer lease term options.

div.div: Room dimensions, square footage, and features shown on the floor plan drawings are approximate and may vary between individual apartments that have similar layouts. Furniture shown on the floor plan drawings is representative and individual apartments come unfurnished unless specified otherwise. Quoted rent is per month for new move-ins to the community, based on the move-in date selected. Pricing may vary based on lease term. Quoted rent does not including other fees and charges that may be part of your lease (i.e. utilities, parking, etc.). Please contact the community for details. Prior to signing a lease, quoted rent, specials, availability, and other terms and conditions are subject to change without notice.
